    "body": "Hi @stevenvandemoortele,\r\n\r\nThanks for the suggestion.\r\n\r\nIn the first place, we plan to provide a sandbox of our new [Autocomplete](https://github.com/algolia/autocomplete) library with Google Maps in a near future.\r\n\r\nIt is not planned yet to provide a widget for InstantSearch but we will definitely keep that in mind!",
