    "body": "For now, https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/discussions/4764 and https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/discussions/4904 will be where this would be discussed. In a future major version, the places widget will be removed, but likely without an alternative, as it had low usage",
